
A monitor is an output device that displays video, images, and text on it's screen. 
It usually shows the work goning on in side a computer system.
Monitor can be connected with computer through various cables like HDMI, USB-C, VGA, and DisplayPort etc. 
Here VGA port is more common method to connect monitor with PC.
Monitor is usually connected with the mother board of the computer.
We can change various options and functions in a computer with the help of the monitor.
Without it the computer is paralyzed, we also cannot run it properly without monitor. 

